            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="lesson">
            <span class="lesson__n">04</span>
            <p class="lesson__t">
              A fast AI-augmented workflow that let one person take a whole product from re-think
              to a complete, consistent system.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="lesson">
            <span class="lesson__n">05</span>
            <p class="lesson__t">
